      "text": "As the founder of Flair, Donna Dixson brings\u00a0integrity, authenticity and enthusiasm to every project. Detail oriented and results driven, she brings marketing savvy, creativity\u00a0and a commitment to alignment into the challenging world of effective sponsorship relationships. Donna's\u00a0extensive network of trusted colleagues add extra value, talent and experience to her work with clients.",
